      <title>众议院通过政府停摆期限临近之际的拨款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-passes-plan-to-fund-government-as-shutdown-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院通过了一项拨款法案，以维持美国政府运转至三月中旬，而就在午夜政府关门期限前几个小时，这一法案结束了动荡的两天，在这两天里，众议院议长迈克·约翰逊先前推行的两项计划均告失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-passes-plan-to-fund-government-as-shutdown-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 23:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币公司 Kraken、Ripple、Ondo 为特朗普就职典礼捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/kraken-ripple-ondo-finance-donate-to-trump-vance-inaugural-committee-xrp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币公司承诺向当选总统的就职委员会捐款，以加大对唐纳德·特朗普的财政支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/kraken-ripple-ondo-finance-donate-to-trump-vance-inaugural-committee-xrp</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 22:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的间谍人选加巴德面临参议院支持的艰难挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-s-spy-pick-gabbard-faces-a-tricky-climb-for-senate-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提名塔尔西·加巴德负责监督美国情报部门，本周她访问了国会山，希望安抚一些迄今为止尚未支持她的共和党参议员，并呼吁任何可能被说服支持她的民主党人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-s-spy-pick-gabbard-faces-a-tricky-climb-for-senate-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 22:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉承诺警惕采取新财政措施的必要性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/lula-says-he-ll-stay-vigilant-on-need-for-new-fiscal-measures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦表示，巴西政府已采取措施维护巴西的财政规则，并重申支持新任央行行长加布里埃尔·加利波罗，这是加利波罗接受紧急手术返回巴西利亚后首次公开发表评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/lula-says-he-ll-stay-vigilant-on-need-for-new-fiscal-measures</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:58:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国政府关门威胁 Rivian 和 Plug 贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/us-loans-to-rivian-plug-under-threat-from-federal-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国政府可能关门，Rivian Automotive Inc.、Plug Power Inc.、PG&amp;E Corp. 和其他公司的数十亿美元联邦贷款面临威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/us-loans-to-rivian-plug-under-threat-from-federal-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默任命彼得·曼德尔森为下一任英国驻美国大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/starmer-names-peter-mandelson-as-uk-ambassador-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 已确认任命贸易专家、工党资深人士彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 为英国下一任驻华盛顿大使。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/starmer-names-peter-mandelson-as-uk-ambassador-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新民主党撤回支持 特鲁多政府面临垮台风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多的一位前重要盟友表示，他将投票推翻政府，此举可能会导致加拿大在明年初陷入选举，除非总理寻求暂时中止议会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西的哈达德认为国会通过紧缩计划几乎不会受到影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/brazil-s-haddad-sees-austerity-plan-nearly-unscathed-by-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西财政部长表示，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的紧缩计划已获巴西国会批准，但该计划的一些变化将仅使巴西的潜在储蓄减少 10 亿雷亚尔（1.64 亿美元），这一数字远低于人们的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/brazil-s-haddad-sees-austerity-plan-nearly-unscathed-by-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院投票开始后，马斯克支持约翰逊计划避免政府关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的主要顾问伊隆·马斯克支持众议院议长迈克·约翰逊第三次尝试支出计划，这在周五晚间开始的投票中提升了该计划通过的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 13:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国法院判处 8 名涉嫌斩首教师的嫌疑人有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-20/verdicts-expected-for-8-people-on-trial-over-their-role-in-the-beheading-of-a-teacher-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎（美联社）——法国反恐法庭周五判处八名涉嫌四年前在巴黎附近的学校外斩首教师塞缪尔·帕蒂的嫌疑人有罪，这起惨无人道的死亡事件震惊了整个法国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-20/verdicts-expected-for-8-people-on-trial-over-their-role-in-the-beheading-of-a-teacher-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 10:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
